<p style="font-size: 16px; color: #374151;">Hi <%= @user.first_name %>,</p>

<p style="font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280; line-height: 1.6;">
  Thanks for joining RezumFit! You're all set to start optimizing your resume with AI and landing more interviews.
</p>

<p style="font-size: 14px; color: #374151; font-weight: 600;">Here's how to get started:</p>

<table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin: 24px 0;">
  <tr>
    <td style="padding-bottom: 16px;">
      <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0"><tr>
        <td style="background: #eff6ff; color: #2563eb; font-weight: bold; width: 28px; height: 28px; border-radius: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: middle; padding-right: 0;">1</td>
        <td style="padding-left: 12px;">
          <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px; color: #374151; font-weight: 600;">Upload your resume</p>
          <p style="margin: 4px 0 0; font-size: 13px; color: #6b7280;">PDF, DOCX, or TXT — we'll extract and parse it instantly.</p>
        </td>
      </tr></table>
    </td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td style="padding-bottom: 16px;">
      <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0"><tr>
        <td style="background: #eff6ff; color: #2563eb; font-weight: bold; width: 28px; height: 28px; border-radius: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: middle;">2</td>
        <td style="padding-left: 12px;">
          <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px; color: #374151; font-weight: 600;">Paste a job description</p>
          <p style="margin: 4px 0 0; font-size: 13px; color: #6b7280;">Our AI tailors your resume specifically for the role.</p>
        </td>
      </tr></table>
    </td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td>
      <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0"><tr>
        <td style="background: #eff6ff; color: #2563eb; font-weight: bold; width: 28px; height: 28px; border-radius: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: middle;">3</td>
        <td style="padding-left: 12px;">
          <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px; color: #374151; font-weight: 600;">Get your optimized resume</p>
          <p style="margin: 4px 0 0; font-size: 13px; color: #6b7280;">See your ATS score improvement and download in PDF/DOCX.</p>
        </td>
      </tr></table>
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>

<p style="font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280;">
  You have <strong style="color: #2563eb;"><%= @user.credits_remaining %> free credits</strong> to get started. Resume optimization uses 2 credits, cover letters use 1 credit.
</p>

<div style="text-align: center; margin: 32px 0 16px;">
  <a href="<%= dashboard_url %>" class="btn-primary" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2563eb, #7c3aed); color: #ffffff; padding: 12px 32px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; display: inline-block;">
    Go to Dashboard
  </a>
</div>
